    <item>
      <title>以下是英格兰银行可以采取的利率措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-09/here-s-what-the-bank-of-england-could-do-on-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计英国央行将把贷款利率维持在 5.25%，但问题是行长安德鲁·贝利 (Andrew Bailey) 是否会就央行何时能够将借贷成本从 16 年来的最高水平降低的问题发出更强的信号。我们的首席英国经济学家 Dan Hanson 与 Caroline Hepker 和 Stephen Carroll 在 Bloomberg Radio 进行了讨论。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-09/here-s-what-the-bank-of-england-could-do-on-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 09:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西历史性洪水为卢拉总统任期创造了“卡特里娜飓风时刻”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/brazil-s-historic-floods-are-a-hurricane-katrina-moment-for-lula-s-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 飞越淹没该国南部地区的洪水时，他不仅调查了造成至少 100 人死亡、16 万人流离失所的灾难，而且调查了他总统任期的决定性时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/brazil-s-historic-floods-are-a-hurricane-katrina-moment-for-lula-s-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其通胀预测上调，政策偏见仍然偏强硬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/turkish-central-bank-raises-inflation-outlook-that-shapes-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行上调了年底通胀预期，并表示准备在必要时进一步收紧货币政策，物价涨幅接近高达75%的峰值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/turkish-central-bank-raises-inflation-outlook-that-shapes-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 08:04:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
